AMAX Inc said it has acceptedoffers to buy its share and option interests in &lt;AustralianConsolidated Minerals Ltd>.    AMAX said the sale is part of its ongoing program toincrease shareholder value.    The company did not identify who made the offer, but saidthe interests involved include 35.2 mln Australian Consolidatedshares to be sold for 6.32 Australian dlrs per share and 5.4mln options to be sold for 4.82 Australian dlrs per option. Reuter&#3;